    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You wake up alone on a spaceship, in front of a terminal with words on it. You're expected to type, so you type. You keep typing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Typing Stars is a relaxing, typing speed and skill based game set in space. Improve your typing dexterity, race against the clock and beat your friends scores. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The AI is very helpful. The AI says that this is for your own good. Please keep typing to validate your viability.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316570/extras/6f48e47f913744d169c0651c3b898884.poster.avif?t=1772039713\" width=1138 height=624 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316570/extras/6f48e47f913744d169c0651c3b898884.webm?t=1772039713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316570/extras/6f48e47f913744d169c0651c3b898884.mp4?t=1772039713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple Typing challenges to play. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leaderboard to compete globally and with your friends.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Children mode to help teach typing without the story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A completely normal and helpful AI system</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't look at the clock.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >h̸̢̙͙͈̦͒̍̄͆e̴̡͔͈̣̳͉̍͗͆l̴̨̘̣̘͕͚p̶̨̬͉̰̎̈̍͑<